---
import logo from "../images/dog.jpg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

---
<section class="container mx-auto mt-4 p-4 gap-8 lg:mt-20">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:gap-40">
    <div class="lg:pe-6 my-auto">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 leading-tight xl:text-5xl">
        Your Local Pet Care Specialist
      </h1>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold leading-tight xl:text2xl mb-6">
        Serving the Southern Highlands since 2019
      </h2>
      <div class="relative w-full sm:w-auto cursor-pointer rounded-2xl">
        <p class="text-xl">
          Welcome to our pet-loving hub in Hill Top, serving the Southern
          Highlands and Wollondilly areas! üêæ We specialize in drop-in pet care
          services, offering high-quality and affordable options. From quick
          check-ins to playful doggy adventures, we're here to make your pets'
          days brighter. Whether you're away for the day, need a break, or want
          some extra support, count on us for reliable drop-in care. Your pets'
          well-being is our top priority, ensuring they're happy and cared for
          in the comfort of their own home. Let us bring joy to your pets' day
          and peace to your mind!
        </p>
        <p>
          Please note: We are not a boarding facility and do not offer this
          service.
        </p>
        <div>
          <button
            class="mt-8 bg-indigo-700 text-white text-xl rounded-full px-6 py-4 shadow-gray-500 shadow-lg"
            >Get In Touch</button
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <Image src={logo} alt="logo" class="rounded-2xl float-end"  />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
